Now Silver Sword's here, too?

00:06.660 --> 00:07.990
Look, another one!

00:07.990 --> 00:09.160
Seriously?

00:09.160 --> 00:13.490
<i>There are many guilds, with many different goals.</i>

00:14.860 --> 00:18.790
<i>There are combat guilds, 
whose primary goal is to get stronger.</i>

00:19.550 --> 00:21.790
<i>In Akihabara, the major ones are</i>

