<i>D.D.D.,</i>

00:24.920 --> 00:26.780
<b>Black Sword Knights 
Player Count 
186 Players</b>

00:25.140 --> 00:26.230
<i>the Black Sword Knights,</i>

00:26.980 --> 00:29.290
<b>Honesty 
Player Count 
743 Players</b>

00:27.630 --> 00:28.580
<i>Honesty,</i>

00:29.500 --> 00:31.790
<b>West Wind Brigade 
Player Count 
64 Players</b>

00:30.050 --> 00:31.310
<i>the West Wind Brigade,</i>

00:34.050 --> 00:36.290
<b>Silver Sword 
Player Count 
220 Players</b>

00:34.260 --> 00:35.390
<i>Silver Sword.</i>

00:36.850 --> 00:39.310
<i>There are also crafting guilds,</i>

00:39.310 --> 00:43.240
<i>whose time is primarily occupied by 
amassing items or selling them in town.</i>

00:44.540 --> 00:46.800
<b>Marine Agency 
Player Count 
2,547 Players</b>

00:45.370 --> 00:46.420
<i>Marine Agency,</i>

